    "description": "拿上你的相机，叫上朋友，准备好一款比你说“茄子！”还快升级的派对游戏吧！<br><br><strong>The Bucketlist Tourist</strong> 是一款多人摄影冒险游戏，每个人都试图拍出完美照片。<br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001640/extras/16f633ca1ddf144ccd66cfeea02bdae6.poster.avif?t=1771607941\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001640/extras/16f633ca1ddf144ccd66cfeea02bdae6.webm?t=1771607941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001640/extras/16f633ca1ddf144ccd66cfeea02bdae6.mp4?t=1771607941\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br>使用遥控快门和有限的尝试次数，你将探索充满活力、色彩丰富的场景，这些场景灵感来源于现实世界的知名景点。任务有时创意十足，有时混乱不堪，有时荒诞搞笑。<br><br>每轮结束后，你的照片将被评审。拍摄最佳照片、度过最精彩假期的玩家将被誉为终极 Bucketlist 冠军。<br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001640/extras/d32b274556746c8c800b6a6286a9685e.poster.avif?t=1771607941\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001640/extras/d32b274556746c8c800b6a6286a9685e.webm?t=1771607941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001640/extras/d32b274556746c8c800b6a6286a9685e.mp4?t=1771607941\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><strong>特点</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>沙发合作模式:</strong> 一起坐在沙发上，享受混乱而欢乐的游戏体验。<br></li><li><strong>照片，照片，再照片:</strong> 尽情拍摄 — 完美作品或搞笑失败都无妨。<br></li><li><strong>多彩的旅行地:</strong> 探索灵感来自著名地标的独特场景。<br></li><li><strong>Bucketlist 挑战:</strong> 迎接创意、疯狂且有时出人意料的任务。<br></li><li><strong>主动布娃娃物理:</strong> 产生不可预测、滑稽的姿势，使每张照片都独一无二。</li></ul><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001640/extras/89c6252927593a23d3939f117feab1fc.poster.avif?t=1771607941\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001640/extras/89c6252927593a23d3939f117feab1fc.webm?t=1771607941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001640/extras/89c6252927593a23d3939f117feab1fc.mp4?t=1771607941\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>轻松上手:</strong> 简单操作，人人都能玩。<br></li><li><strong>拍照奖励:</strong> 优秀照片可获得游戏货币，解锁服装、配饰等。<br></li><li><strong>随心所欲地玩:</strong> 竞赛或合作，根据心情选择。<br></li><li><strong>你的游客，你的风格:</strong> 自定义角色服装。<br></li><li><strong>永远有新内容:</strong> 免费更新定期带来新场景、新任务和新内容。<br></li><li><strong>高分挑战:</strong> 不断刷新分数，并与社区分享最佳照片。<br></li><li><strong>与我们一起成长:</strong> 提供反馈 — 我们与玩家一起开发游戏。</li></ul>",
